OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fcloudy through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight with mainly light rain, but
OL,8,Fthis will turn heavier and more
OL,9,Fpersistent at times in the southwest.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FA cloudy day with occasional
OL,12,Frain and drizzle, this mainly across
OL,13,Fthe north. Chance of a little
OL,14,Fbrightness at times along the east
OL,15,Fcoast. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
