OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA
OL,6,Fchangeable, often cloudy and breezy
OL,7,Ffew days with spells of rain,
OL,8,Fpersistent at times in the west, but
OL,9,Fdrier in the east with some bright
OL,10,Fspells possible.
